txt.en: Gúrkug and goblins can be found in Máttugard.\n\nYou should defeat goblins.
You have defeated Gúrkug and assisted those who wish to reclaim Gundabad.

The bounty notice reads:

'Who among you has the courage to face Gúrkug? The brutal goblin driver wields his drudges as throwing spears, swarming in on any in his way.

'A reward to any who can defeat Gúrkug and other goblins in Máttugard!'
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Gúrkug, a brutal goblin driver found in Máttugard.
